街段–小合併組（英文名稱）: Name of Small Street Block Group (in English)
街段–小合併組（中文名稱）: Name of Small Street Block Group (in Chinese)

街段–小合併組（英文名稱）: 為顧及數據的精確度及保障個別受訪者的私隱，人數少的街段會與鄰近的街段合併為「街段–小合併組」或「街段–大合併組」後才發布統計數字。「街段–小合併組」及「街段–大合併組」的人口分別為最少400人及最少1 000人。

Having regard to data precision and protection of data privacy of individual respondents, a Street Block with a small population is merged with adjacent Street Block(s) as a Small Street Block Group or Large Street Block Group for the release of statistics.  There are at least 400 persons and at least 1 000 persons in a Small Street Block Group and a Large Street Block Group respectively.
